{
  "video_id": "uJr4wGcLNsA",
  "title": "Our fight for disability rights -- and why we're not done yet | Judith Heumann",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 15840.0,
      "text": "I was born in 1947, a long time ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17280.0,
      "end_time": 21400.0,
      "text": "and when I was 18 months old, I had polio."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21680.0,
      "end_time": 24576.0,
      "text": "I was in an iron lung for three months"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24600.0,
      "end_time": 27120.0,
      "text": "and in and out of the hospital for three years."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27960.0,
      "end_time": 31376.0,
      "text": "Now, we had lots of neighbors in our Brooklyn neighborhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31400.0,
      "end_time": 34720.0,
      "text": "and some of them were really very helpful for my parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35320.0,
      "end_time": 39160.0,
      "text": "Some of them were really afraid of contagion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39400.0,
      "end_time": 42256.0,
      "text": "and they wouldn&#39;t even walk in front of our house."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42280.0,
      "end_time": 45800.0,
      "text": "They would literally walk across the street."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45680.0,
      "end_time": 50656.0,
      "text": "I think this was a time when my family really began to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 50680.0,
      "end_time": 53136.0,
      "text": "what disability meant to some people:"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 53160.0,
      "end_time": 54360.0,
      "text": "fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55800.0,
      "end_time": 59376.0,
      "text": "And it wasn&#39;t even a sure thing that I would live at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59400.0,
      "end_time": 62736.0,
      "text": "although I didn&#39;t learn about this until I was 36 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 62760.0,
      "end_time": 65655.0,
      "text": "I was having a discussion with my father one night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65680.0,
      "end_time": 68696.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"You know, when you were two years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68720.0,
      "end_time": 71136.0,
      "text": "one of the doctors suggested to your mom and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 71160.0,
      "end_time": 74960.0,
      "text": "that you live in an institution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74120.0,
      "end_time": 76976.0,
      "text": "that they could just go ahead with their lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77000.0,
      "end_time": 78256.0,
      "text": "and raise their kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78280.0,
      "end_time": 83296.0,
      "text": "and kind of be done with having to deal with all the disability-related things."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 83320.0,
      "end_time": 87416.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t believe my father, not because he was a liar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 87440.0,
      "end_time": 89776.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;d never heard this story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 89800.0,
      "end_time": 92960.0,
      "text": "and my mother in fact validated that."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92120.0,
      "end_time": 94256.0,
      "text": "She never wanted to tell me."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94280.0,
      "end_time": 98816.0,
      "text": "But in reality, I don&#39;t know why I was really surprised by this story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 98840.0,
      "end_time": 101616.0,
      "text": "because when I was five years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 101640.0,
      "end_time": 105896.0,
      "text": "and my mother, like mothers and fathers all across the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 105920.0,
      "end_time": 108696.0,
      "text": "was taking me to school to enroll,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108720.0,
      "end_time": 113560.0,
      "text": "she pushed my wheelchair to the school in walking distance to our house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 113800.0,
      "end_time": 116176.0,
      "text": "pulled the wheelchair up the steps into the school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 116200.0,
      "end_time": 118376.0,
      "text": "and we were greeted by the principal."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 118400.0,
      "end_time": 120256.0,
      "text": "Not really greeted."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120280.0,
      "end_time": 124856.0,
      "text": "But the principal said, no, I couldn&#39;t come to that school"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124880.0,
      "end_time": 127576.0,
      "text": "because it wasn&#39;t accessible."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 127600.0,
      "end_time": 129976.0,
      "text": "But he told us not to worry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130000.0,
      "end_time": 135176.0,
      "text": "because the Board of Education in fact would send a teacher to my house."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 135200.0,
      "end_time": 137160.0,
      "text": "And they did"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 137400.0,
      "end_time": 140734.0,
      "text": "for a total of two and a half hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140759.0,
      "end_time": 141976.0,
      "text": "a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 142000.0,
      "end_time": 143256.0,
      "text": "(Audience murmurs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 143280.0,
      "end_time": 145336.0,
      "text": "But for good behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145360.0,
      "end_time": 148376.0,
      "text": "they threw in an occupational therapist"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 148400.0,
      "end_time": 151256.0,
      "text": "who taught me that very essential skill"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 151280.0,
      "end_time": 152720.0,
      "text": "of cross-stitching."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153280.0,
      "end_time": 154536.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154560.0,
      "end_time": 155896.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t cross-stitch today."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155920.0,
      "end_time": 158296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158320.0,
      "end_time": 162160.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t actually get to go to school in a real building"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162400.0,
      "end_time": 164176.0,
      "text": "until I was nine years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164200.0,
      "end_time": 167375.0,
      "text": "and then I was in classes only with disabled children"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167400.0,
      "end_time": 170616.0,
      "text": "in a school that had mainly nondisabled children."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170640.0,
      "end_time": 172495.0,
      "text": "And in my classes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 172520.0,
      "end_time": 175720.0,
      "text": "there were students up to the age of 21."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176840.0,
      "end_time": 178696.0,
      "text": "And then, after 21,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 178720.0,
      "end_time": 182560.0,
      "text": "they went to something called sheltered workshops"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 182800.0,
      "end_time": 183696.0,
      "text": "with menial work"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 183720.0,
      "end_time": 186920.0,
      "text": "and earning either nothing or below minimum wage."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 187480.0,
      "end_time": 190576.0,
      "text": "So I understood discrimination."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 190600.0,
      "end_time": 193376.0,
      "text": "My parents understood discrimination."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 193400.0,
      "end_time": 196160.0,
      "text": "My parents came from Germany."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 196400.0,
      "end_time": 199736.0,
      "text": "They were German Jews who left in the 1930s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 199760.0,
      "end_time": 201239.0,
      "text": "escaping the Holocaust."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 201920.0,
      "end_time": 205335.0,
      "text": "My parents lost family and they lost parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 205360.0,
      "end_time": 209136.0,
      "text": "Both my parents lost their parents in the Holocaust."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 209160.0,
      "end_time": 211335.0,
      "text": "And so they realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 211360.0,
      "end_time": 213456.0,
      "text": "that they could not be silent"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 213480.0,
      "end_time": 216160.0,
      "text": "as things were going wrong for me in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 216920.0,
      "end_time": 218296.0,
      "text": "Not me personally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 218320.0,
      "end_time": 220656.0,
      "text": "but what was going on around me."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 220680.0,
      "end_time": 223976.0,
      "text": "They learned that because I used a wheelchair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 224000.0,
      "end_time": 227816.0,
      "text": "none of the high schools in New York City, in the entire city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 227840.0,
      "end_time": 229736.0,
      "text": "were wheelchair accessible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 229760.0,
      "end_time": 232256.0,
      "text": "so what was supposed to happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 232280.0,
      "end_time": 235536.0,
      "text": "is I was supposed to go back onto home instruction"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 235560.0,
      "end_time": 238960.0,
      "text": "along with many other students."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 238120.0,
      "end_time": 243296.0,
      "text": "So my parents banded together with other parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 243320.0,
      "end_time": 245416.0,
      "text": "They went to the Board of Education"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 245440.0,
      "end_time": 249936.0,
      "text": "and they demanded that the Board of Ed make some of the high schools accessible."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 249960.0,
      "end_time": 251616.0,
      "text": "And they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 251640.0,
      "end_time": 254160.0,
      "text": "And so I and many others"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 254400.0,
      "end_time": 257935.0,
      "text": "were finally able to go to high school, a regular high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 257959.0,
      "end_time": 259560.0,
      "text": "and take regular classes."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 260519.0,
      "end_time": 262719.0,
      "text": "So what happened next?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263440.0,
      "end_time": 266856.0,
      "text": "I was learning more and more about what discrimination was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 266880.0,
      "end_time": 271159.0,
      "text": "and equally important, I was learning that I needed to become my own advocate."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 271920.0,
      "end_time": 275376.0,
      "text": "I was entering college, Long Island University,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 275400.0,
      "end_time": 277816.0,
      "text": "and I had always wanted to be a teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 277840.0,
      "end_time": 283560.0,
      "text": "and so I minored in education and I took all the appropriate courses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 283800.0,
      "end_time": 286976.0,
      "text": "and then when it was time for me to go for my license,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 287000.0,
      "end_time": 289656.0,
      "text": "I had to take a written exam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 289680.0,
      "end_time": 291336.0,
      "text": "an oral exam"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 291360.0,
      "end_time": 293296.0,
      "text": "and a medical exam."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 293320.0,
      "end_time": 296536.0,
      "text": "At that time, all three of those exams"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 296560.0,
      "end_time": 300216.0,
      "text": "were given in completely inaccessible buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 300240.0,
      "end_time": 304496.0,
      "text": "so I had friends who carried me up and down the steps"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 304520.0,
      "end_time": 306960.0,
      "text": "for these exams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 306120.0,
      "end_time": 307776.0,
      "text": "not in a motorized wheelchair."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 307800.0,
      "end_time": 308816.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 308840.0,
      "end_time": 310320.0,
      "text": "In a manual wheelchair."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 311440.0,
      "end_time": 314216.0,
      "text": "But I passed my oral exam."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 314240.0,
      "end_time": 316400.0,
      "text": "I passed my written exam."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 316960.0,
      "end_time": 320640.0,
      "text": "My medical exam was something completely different."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 321600.0,
      "end_time": 324736.0,
      "text": "One of the first questions the doctor asked me"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 324760.0,
      "end_time": 330390.0,
      "text": "was, could I please show her how I went to the bathroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 331720.0,
      "end_time": 333696.0,
      "text": "I was 22 years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 333720.0,
      "end_time": 336296.0,
      "text": "and you know when you go for any kind of an interview,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 336320.0,
      "end_time": 339575.0,
      "text": "you think about all the kinds of questions that people could ask you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 339600.0,
      "end_time": 341296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 341320.0,
      "end_time": 342560.0,
      "text": "That was not one of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 343880.0,
      "end_time": 346456.0,
      "text": "And I was freaked out in the first place"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 346480.0,
      "end_time": 347936.0,
      "text": "because I had heard"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 347960.0,
      "end_time": 351455.0,
      "text": "that there were actually no disabled people using wheelchairs"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 351480.0,
      "end_time": 353136.0,
      "text": "who were teachers in New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 353160.0,
      "end_time": 357336.0,
      "text": "so each step along the way I was expecting something bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 357360.0,
      "end_time": 359256.0,
      "text": "So I said to her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 359280.0,
      "end_time": 361775.0,
      "text": "is it a requirement that teachers show their students"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 361800.0,
      "end_time": 363800.0,
      "text": "how to go to the bathroom?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 364200.0,
      "end_time": 366200.0,
      "text": "If it is, I can do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 367400.0,
      "end_time": 369616.0,
      "text": "So no surprise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 369640.0,
      "end_time": 371376.0,
      "text": "I was failed"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 371400.0,
      "end_time": 373816.0,
      "text": "because I didn&#39;t pass the medical."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 373840.0,
      "end_time": 377135.0,
      "text": "The official reason that I was denied my job"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 377160.0,
      "end_time": 383976.0,
      "text": "was paralysis of poliomyelitis sequelae of -- I&#39;m sorry."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 384000.0,
      "end_time": 388536.0,
      "text": "Paralysis of both lower limbs, sequelae of poliomyelitis."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 388560.0,
      "end_time": 391176.0,
      "text": "Honestly, I didn&#39;t know what the word \"sequelae\" meant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 391200.0,
      "end_time": 394496.0,
      "text": "so I went to the dictionary, and it meant \"because of.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 394520.0,
      "end_time": 397719.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d been denied my license because I couldn&#39;t walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 398600.0,
      "end_time": 401176.0,
      "text": "So what was I going to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 401200.0,
      "end_time": 404256.0,
      "text": "This is a really important time in my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 404280.0,
      "end_time": 406215.0,
      "text": "because it would be the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 406240.0,
      "end_time": 410736.0,
      "text": "that I really would be challenging the system, me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 410760.0,
      "end_time": 414496.0,
      "text": "and although I was working with a lot of other friends who had disabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 414520.0,
      "end_time": 417960.0,
      "text": "who were encouraging me to move forward with this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 417120.0,
      "end_time": 419696.0,
      "text": "it was nonetheless quite frightening."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 419720.0,
      "end_time": 421296.0,
      "text": "But I was really very lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 421320.0,
      "end_time": 425536.0,
      "text": "I had a friend who was a disabled student at Long Island University"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 425560.0,
      "end_time": 428816.0,
      "text": "and was also a stringer at the \"New York Times,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 428840.0,
      "end_time": 431496.0,
      "text": "and he was able to get a reporter"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 431520.0,
      "end_time": 435416.0,
      "text": "to write a really good piece about what had happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 435440.0,
      "end_time": 437840.0,
      "text": "and why he thought what had happened was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 438600.0,
      "end_time": 443136.0,
      "text": "The next day there was an editorial in the \"New York Times\""
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 443160.0,
      "end_time": 446456.0,
      "text": "with the title of \"Heumann v. The Board of Education\""
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 446480.0,
      "end_time": 448776.0,
      "text": "and the \"New York Times\" came out in support"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 448800.0,
      "end_time": 450896.0,
      "text": "of my getting my teaching license."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 450920.0,
      "end_time": 454816.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 454840.0,
      "end_time": 456176.0,
      "text": "And then the same day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 456200.0,
      "end_time": 461560.0,
      "text": "I got a call from an attorney who was writing a book about civil rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 461800.0,
      "end_time": 464376.0,
      "text": "And he was calling me to interview me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 464400.0,
      "end_time": 466575.0,
      "text": "and I was interviewing him."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 466600.0,
      "end_time": 467896.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t know that."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 467920.0,
      "end_time": 470656.0,
      "text": "And at the end of our discussion, I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 470680.0,
      "end_time": 474616.0,
      "text": "\"Would you be willing to represent me? I want to sue the Board of Education.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 474640.0,
      "end_time": 476256.0,
      "text": "And he said yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 476280.0,
      "end_time": 481816.0,
      "text": "Now, sometimes I say that the stars were aligned around this court case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 481840.0,
      "end_time": 485296.0,
      "text": "because we had an amazing judge:"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 485320.0,
      "end_time": 490536.0,
      "text": "the first African American female federal judge --"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 490560.0,
      "end_time": 492216.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 492240.0,
      "end_time": 494736.0,
      "text": "Constance Baker Motley."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 494760.0,
      "end_time": 500695.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 500720.0,
      "end_time": 504656.0,
      "text": "And she knew discrimination when she saw it."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 504680.0,
      "end_time": 507256.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 507280.0,
      "end_time": 511256.0,
      "text": "So she strongly encouraged the Board of Ed"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 511280.0,
      "end_time": 514576.0,
      "text": "to give me another medical exam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 514600.0,
      "end_time": 516296.0,
      "text": "which they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 516320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519336.00000000006,
      "text": "And then I got my license,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 519360.0,
      "end_time": 521960.0,
      "text": "and while it took a number of months"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 521120.0,
      "end_time": 524176.0,
      "text": "for me to actually get a principal to offer me a job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 524200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 528960.0,
      "text": "I finally did get a job and I started teaching that fall"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 528120.0,
      "end_time": 531560.0,
      "text": "in the same school that I had gone to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 531800.0,
      "end_time": 532280.0,
      "text": "second grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 533400.0,
      "end_time": 534616.0,
      "text": "So --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 534640.0,
      "end_time": 538175.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 538200.0,
      "end_time": 539776.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a whole other TED Talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 539800.0,
      "end_time": 541415.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 541440.0,
      "end_time": 545496.0,
      "text": "But I was learning as my friends were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 545520.0,
      "end_time": 548160.0,
      "text": "and people I didn&#39;t know around the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 548400.0,
      "end_time": 551295.0,
      "text": "that we had to be our own advocates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 551320.0,
      "end_time": 555576.0,
      "text": "that we needed to fight back people&#39;s view"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 555600.0,
      "end_time": 558936.0,
      "text": "that if you had a disability, you needed to be cured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 558960.0,
      "end_time": 562160.0,
      "text": "that equality was not part of the equation."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 562400.0,
      "end_time": 565336.0,
      "text": "And we were learning from the Civil Rights Movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 565360.0,
      "end_time": 567496.0,
      "text": "and from the Women&#39;s Rights Movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 567520.0,
      "end_time": 570696.0,
      "text": "We were learning from them about their activism"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 570720.0,
      "end_time": 572736.0,
      "text": "and their ability to come together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 572760.0,
      "end_time": 575496.0,
      "text": "not only to discuss problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 575520.0,
      "end_time": 577456.0,
      "text": "but to discuss solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 577480.0,
      "end_time": 581880.0,
      "text": "And what was born is what we call today the Disability Rights Movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 582800.0,
      "end_time": 585599.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d like to tell you a couple of riddles."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 586840.0,
      "end_time": 589800.0,
      "text": "How many people do you think it takes"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 590800.0,
      "end_time": 593856.0,
      "text": "to stop traffic on Madison Avenue"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 593880.0,
      "end_time": 596415.0,
      "text": "during rush hour in New York City?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 596440.0,
      "end_time": 598560.0,
      "text": "Do you have a guess? How many?"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 598800.0,
      "end_time": 599795.0,
      "text": "(Audience members shout out answers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 601360.0,
      "end_time": 602560.0,
      "text": "Fifty."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 603520.0,
      "end_time": 604720.0,
      "text": "One would be too little."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 606160.0,
      "end_time": 607415.0,
      "text": "Fifty people."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 607440.0,
      "end_time": 610176.0,
      "text": "And there were no accessible paddy wagons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 610200.0,
      "end_time": 612936.0,
      "text": "so they had to just kind of deal with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 612960.0,
      "end_time": 615256.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 615280.0,
      "end_time": 617256.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 617280.0,
      "end_time": 619616.0,
      "text": "But let me tell you another riddle."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 619640.0,
      "end_time": 624336.0,
      "text": "How many people does it take to stop a bus in New York City"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 624360.0,
      "end_time": 627920.0,
      "text": "when they refuse to let you on because you&#39;re in a wheelchair?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 629120.0,
      "end_time": 631496.0,
      "text": "One. That is the right answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 631520.0,
      "end_time": 634415.0,
      "text": "So what you have to do though"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 634440.0,
      "end_time": 636296.0,
      "text": "is take your wheelchair --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 636320.0,
      "end_time": 639296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 639320.0,
      "end_time": 643176.0,
      "text": "Sidle in the right place right in front of the steps"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 643200.0,
      "end_time": 646536.0,
      "text": "and give it a little push underneath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 646560.0,
      "end_time": 648335.0,
      "text": "and then their bus can&#39;t move."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 648360.0,
      "end_time": 652160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 652400.0,
      "end_time": 655575.0,
      "text": "Any of you who want to learn how to do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 655600.0,
      "end_time": 656816.0,
      "text": "talk to me after this."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 656840.0,
      "end_time": 658656.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 658680.0,
      "end_time": 664920.0,
      "text": "In 1972, President Nixon vetoed the Rehabilitation Act."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 665720.0,
      "end_time": 668360.0,
      "text": "We protested. He signed it."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 669120.0,
      "end_time": 674960.0,
      "text": "Then the regulations that needed to be promulgated to implement that law"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 674120.0,
      "end_time": 676536.0,
      "text": "had not in fact been signed."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 676560.0,
      "end_time": 678920.0,
      "text": "We demonstrated. They were signed."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 679680.0,
      "end_time": 683536.0,
      "text": "And when the Americans With Disabilities Act, the ADA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 683560.0,
      "end_time": 686575.0,
      "text": "our Emancipation Proclamation Act,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 686600.0,
      "end_time": 692160.0,
      "text": "looked as though it might not in fact be passed in the House or Senate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 692400.0,
      "end_time": 696295.0,
      "text": "disabled people from all across the United States came together"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 696320.0,
      "end_time": 699880.0,
      "text": "and they crawled up the Capitol steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 701560.0,
      "end_time": 704295.0,
      "text": "That was an amazing day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 704320.0,
      "end_time": 707800.0,
      "text": "and the House and Senate passed the ADA."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 708520.0,
      "end_time": 713976.0,
      "text": "And then President Bush signed the ADA."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 714000.0,
      "end_time": 715576.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a great picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 715600.0,
      "end_time": 719656.0,
      "text": "President Bush signed the ADA on the lawn of the White House."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 719680.0,
      "end_time": 721656.0,
      "text": "It was an amazing day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 721680.0,
      "end_time": 724199.0,
      "text": "and there are about 2,000 people there."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 725000.0,
      "end_time": 728960.0,
      "text": "It was July 26, 1990."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 729720.0,
      "end_time": 733416.0,
      "text": "And one of the most famous statements he had in his speech"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 733440.0,
      "end_time": 739400.0,
      "text": "was, \"Let the shameful walls of exclusion finally come tumbling down.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 740000.0,
      "end_time": 742560.0,
      "text": "For any of you in the room"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 742800.0,
      "end_time": 745616.0,
      "text": "who are 50 or older, or maybe or even 40 or older,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 745640.0,
      "end_time": 748816.0,
      "text": "you remember a time when there were no ramps on the streets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 748840.0,
      "end_time": 750896.0,
      "text": "when buses were not accessible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 750920.0,
      "end_time": 752896.0,
      "text": "when trains were not accessible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 752920.0,
      "end_time": 756736.0,
      "text": "where there were no wheelchair-accessible bathrooms in shopping malls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 756760.0,
      "end_time": 759896.0,
      "text": "where you certainly did not have a sign language interpreter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 759920.0,
      "end_time": 764960.0,
      "text": "or captioning, or braille or other kinds of supports."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 764120.0,
      "end_time": 766560.0,
      "text": "These things have changed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 766800.0,
      "end_time": 768736.0,
      "text": "and they have inspired the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 768760.0,
      "end_time": 773576.0,
      "text": "And disabled people around the world want laws like we have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 773600.0,
      "end_time": 775840.0,
      "text": "and they want those laws enforced."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 776600.0,
      "end_time": 779416.0,
      "text": "And so what we&#39;ve seen is something called"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 779440.0,
      "end_time": 782720.0,
      "text": "the Convention on the Rights of Persons with Disabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 783160.0,
      "end_time": 787160.0,
      "text": "It is a treaty that was adopted in 2006."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 787400.0,
      "end_time": 791160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s celebrating is 10-year anniversary."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 791400.0,
      "end_time": 795480.0,
      "text": "More than 165 countries have joined this treaty."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 796160.0,
      "end_time": 800256.0,
      "text": "It is the first international human rights treaty"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 800280.0,
      "end_time": 802839.0,
      "text": "fully focused on disabled people."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 803520.0,
      "end_time": 807656.0,
      "text": "But I am sad to say that our US Senate"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 807680.0,
      "end_time": 812935.0,
      "text": "has failed to recommend to our president that we ratify the treaty."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 812960.0,
      "end_time": 815896.0,
      "text": "We signed it in 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 815920.0,
      "end_time": 820136.0,
      "text": "but it doesn&#39;t come into force until ratification,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 820160.0,
      "end_time": 823376.0,
      "text": "and the president -- no president can ratify a treaty"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 823400.0,
      "end_time": 825959.0,
      "text": "without the consent of the Senate."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 826560.0,
      "end_time": 830160.0,
      "text": "So we feel really strongly"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 830400.0,
      "end_time": 833575.0,
      "text": "that our US Senate needs to do its job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 833600.0,
      "end_time": 837776.0,
      "text": "that our Senate needs to enable us as Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 837800.0,
      "end_time": 842935.0,
      "text": "not only to be able to assist disabled people and governments around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 842960.0,
      "end_time": 846816.0,
      "text": "to learn about the good work that we&#39;ve been doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 846840.0,
      "end_time": 848856.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s equally important"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 848880.0,
      "end_time": 852696.0,
      "text": "that disabled people have the same opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 852720.0,
      "end_time": 856376.0,
      "text": "to travel, study and work abroad"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 856400.0,
      "end_time": 858776.0,
      "text": "as anyone else in our country."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 858800.0,
      "end_time": 862935.0,
      "text": "And as long as many countries don&#39;t have the same laws as we do"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 862960.0,
      "end_time": 865576.0,
      "text": "and don&#39;t enforce them if they have them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 865600.0,
      "end_time": 868680.0,
      "text": "opportunities for disabled people are more limited."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 869840.0,
      "end_time": 871776.0,
      "text": "When I travel abroad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 871800.0,
      "end_time": 874616.0,
      "text": "I am always meeting with disabled women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 874640.0,
      "end_time": 877960.0,
      "text": "and those women tell me stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 877120.0,
      "end_time": 881456.0,
      "text": "about how they experience violence and rape"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 881480.0,
      "end_time": 885136.0,
      "text": "and how in many cases these forms of violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 885160.0,
      "end_time": 890656.0,
      "text": "occur from family members and people that they know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 890680.0,
      "end_time": 893256.0,
      "text": "who in fact may be working for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 893280.0,
      "end_time": 896696.0,
      "text": "And frequently these cases are not adjudicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 896720.0,
      "end_time": 898696.0,
      "text": "I meet disabled people"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 898720.0,
      "end_time": 903376.0,
      "text": "who have been offered jobs by businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 903400.0,
      "end_time": 906776.0,
      "text": "because they live in a country where there&#39;s a quota system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 906800.0,
      "end_time": 909335.0,
      "text": "and in order to avoid a fine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 909360.0,
      "end_time": 911616.0,
      "text": "they will hire you"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 911640.0,
      "end_time": 912896.0,
      "text": "and then tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 912920.0,
      "end_time": 914776.0,
      "text": "\"You don&#39;t need to come to work"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 914800.0,
      "end_time": 917959.0,
      "text": "because we really don&#39;t need you in the facility.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 918800.0,
      "end_time": 921376.0,
      "text": "I have visited institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 921400.0,
      "end_time": 925256.0,
      "text": "where the stench of urine is so strong"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 925280.0,
      "end_time": 928376.0,
      "text": "that before you open the door of your vehicle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 928400.0,
      "end_time": 930415.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re kind of pushed back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 930440.0,
      "end_time": 933256.0,
      "text": "and then gone into those institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 933280.0,
      "end_time": 938175.0,
      "text": "where people should be living in the community with appropriate supports"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 938200.0,
      "end_time": 941256.0,
      "text": "and seen people almost naked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 941280.0,
      "end_time": 943776.0,
      "text": "people who are chemically drugged"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 943800.0,
      "end_time": 946280.0,
      "text": "and people who are living lives of despair."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 947120.0,
      "end_time": 952440.0,
      "text": "These are some of the things that the US needs to be doing more to correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 953240.0,
      "end_time": 956416.0,
      "text": "We know discrimination when we see it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 956440.0,
      "end_time": 958480.0,
      "text": "and we need to be fighting it together."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 959120.0,
      "end_time": 962280.0,
      "text": "So what is it that we can be doing together?"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 963320.0,
      "end_time": 966960.0,
      "text": "I encourage you all to recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 966120.0,
      "end_time": 971280.0,
      "text": "that disability is a family you can join at any point in your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 972400.0,
      "end_time": 976520.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to see by a show of hands how many of you have ever broken a bone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 978800.0,
      "end_time": 983575.0,
      "text": "And then, when you leave today, I&#39;d like you to maybe write a couple of sentences"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 983600.0,
      "end_time": 987456.0,
      "text": "about what that period of time has been like for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 987480.0,
      "end_time": 990160.0,
      "text": "because frequently I hear from people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 990400.0,
      "end_time": 993550.0,
      "text": "\"You know, I couldn&#39;t do this, I couldn&#39;t do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 993800.0,
      "end_time": 997376.0,
      "text": "People talked to me differently. They acted differently towards me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 997400.0,
      "end_time": 1001256.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what I see and other disabled people see"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1001280.0,
      "end_time": 1002839.0,
      "text": "in flashing letters."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1003520.0,
      "end_time": 1006256.0,
      "text": "But we -- you in this room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1006280.0,
      "end_time": 1009496.0,
      "text": "people listening and watching this TED Talk --"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1009520.0,
      "end_time": 1012656.0,
      "text": "together we can make a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1012680.0,
      "end_time": 1015760.0,
      "text": "Together we can speak up for justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 1016280.0,
      "end_time": 1019120.0,
      "text": "Together we can help change the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 1019960.0,
      "end_time": 1022536.0,
      "text": "Thank you. I have to go catch my bus."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 1022560.0,
      "end_time": 1029000.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}